 ;; - Valid Strudel methods and operators include: note, sound, s, n, cutoff, resonance, delay, room, speed, gain, pan, struct, stack, seq, rand, irand, slow, fast, rev, chunk, sometimes, often, rarely, every, off, jux, add, sub, and their chainable equivalents.
